Package: liu
Version: 0.7
Date: 2026-05-16
Title: Lightning Index Units
Description: LIU implements SQL-like indexes for data frames in R. It allows to index columns of data frames by creating light B+trees with pairs key-row_number. This shifts complexity of searching from linear to logaritmic (O(log n)), which makes few other functions (exp. min, max, count, merge) much faster.
